				You know if this game was not run by some deep pockets this idiot of a mother would be forced to face the fact that she FAILED as a parent, instead she can be convinced by some bottom-dweller(read lawyer) that she is due some compensation from SOE/Verant.  Sorry to be callus but this moron's death is the same as the kid's who died acting out sword fights playing D&amp;D.  Darwin's laws at work.  They have a word for people who cannot distiguish reality from fantasy, it is called psychotic.  Yes, this game is very gripping, but today everything is an addiction and it is everyone else's fault that I, you, we, etc. have problems.  As long as we live in  a litginous society where we can all blame other for our problems, we will never get to the root of our problems.  This kid's problem was at home.  The blame for his problems lies squarely on that fat ugly piece of crap that is trying to sue SOE/Verant for her failings, his mother.  I would rather eat worms than defend that money-making faceless and careless  monster called SOE/Verant, but C'mon people, this idiot doesn't respect because he is dead.  &quot;No hero in you tragedy, No daring in your escape, No salute for your surrender, nothing noble in your fate. Christ what have you done?&quot;
				</font>
